description: Rare South Boston City Point three- family with huge upside potential for investors looking to enter a top performing market. 925 East 4th Street consists of over 4,600sq ft of living space with 12 bedrooms, rear yard, 3 private decks and close proximity to Castle Island or M Street Beach. A large partially finished basement might give buyers the possibility of expanding Unit 1 with additional bedrooms or living area. This property has been well maintained and owned by the same family for over 30 years. Schedule your tour today!
